&lt;p&gt;Team Leadership &amp;amp; Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, coach, and develop a high-performing operations organization that delivers consistent execution every day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire, onboard, and grow frontline leaders and team members as Revivn continues to scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set clear expectations, provide frequent coaching and feedback, and create opportunities for people to grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of accountability, safety, ownership, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operations Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own day-to-day execution across receiving, processing, data destruction, testing, and outbound logistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Sr Director of ITAD Operations to set throughput, quality, and SLA targets — and hold the team accountable for hitting them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage staffing plans, schedules, and capacity to meet variable inbound volume without sacrificing quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure every operation remains audit-ready and compliant with Revivn&#39;s security standards, certifications, and safety requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Process Improvement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standardize processes across sites so every operation runs from the same playbook.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify bottlenecks, dig into root causes, and drive measurable improvements in throughput, quality, and cost.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and track operational KPIs, using data to prioritize what gets fixed first.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pilot improvements at one site, prove the results, and scale what works across the operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
