&lt;p&gt;This position is primarily scheduled &lt;strong&gt;Monday through Friday from 7:30am to 4:00pm&lt;/strong&gt;; however, flexibility is essential to meet customer pickup schedules.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overtime is regularly available&lt;/strong&gt; and expected based on business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some pickup routes require an &lt;strong&gt;earlier start time&lt;/strong&gt; than the standard schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regional trips may involve extended workdays, with drivers typically returning &lt;strong&gt;by or before 7:00pm&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasional travel throughout Central California, Greater Los Angeles Area, the Bay Area, and surrounding regions is required.&lt;/li&gt;
