&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with marketing on account research, org mapping, and entry strategies for target accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage an accurate pipeline, forecasting outcomes with clarity and keeping CRM hygiene tight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage and present to senior stakeholders, including IT, finance, and C-level executives through both calls and in-person meetings that require consistent travel&lt;/li&gt;
