&lt;li&gt;Partner with Account Management on a smooth post-sale handoff that sets up long-term expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel required on a monthly basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share market and product insight back to Marketing, RevOps, Product, and Engineering to sharpen our go-to-market&lt;/li&gt;
